  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.header" : "存取物品",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.text_1" : "手持物品右键果盆可存入物品\n注意，果盆只可储存单种物品",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.text_2" : "空手右键果盆可取出1个物品",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.text_3" : "潜行时空手右键果盆可取出所有物品",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.header" : "压榨果汁",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.text_1" : "向果盆内放入可被榨汁的原料",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.text_2" : "在果盆上方跳呀跳呀就能渐渐将原料榨成果汁了",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.text_3" : "然而，如若果盆内的物品无法榨汁，就会被踩得飞散出去",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.header" : "倾斜变体",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.text_1" : "对着墙壁放置果盆会产生倾斜的变体\n倾斜的果盆可以正常存储物品",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.text_2" : "然而，倾斜的果盆无法用于榨汁",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.text_3" : "同样，其内容物也不会被踩得飞散出去",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.header" : "使用酒桶",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_1" : "首先打开顶盖",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_2" : "然后放入流体和可能需要的原料",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_3" : "确认无误后，盖上顶盖",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_4" : "接下来，只需静静等待酒的酿造\n酿造的时间越长，酒的品质越高",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_5" : "右键酒桶可查看酿造进度",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_6" : "在水龙头下放置玻璃瓶，右键水龙头即可将酿好的酒灌入瓶中",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.header" : "野外生成",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_1" : "四处逛逛，你能在野外的树上发现这些葡萄藤\n此外，与蜂巢相似，用骨粉催熟周围有花的树苗，也有概率生成葡萄藤",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_2" : "无需工具，空手破坏即可掉落葡萄藤",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_3" : "葡萄藤可在完整方块和树叶下方种植",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_4" : "以此法种植的葡萄藤会向下生长，但不会结出葡萄",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_5" : "使用剪刀右键可对葡萄藤剪枝，使其不再继续向下生长",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.header" : "种植葡萄",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_1" : "在土壤上方一格的藤架上种植葡萄藤",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_2" : "葡萄藤会优先向上方的藤架生长",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_3" : "然后向四周的藤架蔓延",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_4" : "当长有葡萄藤的藤架下方有空位时，就会开始结出葡萄",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_5" : "葡萄成熟后，空手采摘会掉落1-2个葡萄",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_6" : "用剪刀采摘则会掉落2-3个葡萄",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.tag.brewing" : "酿酒",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.tag.brewing.description" : "从零开始学习酿酒所需要知道的基础知识"
}
